      • registerEntityProgram

        void registerEntityProgram​(String name,
                           EntityProgram program)
        Register an entity program with the given name.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the program; must not be null; must be unique
        program - the program to register; must not be null
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if an argument is null
        ElementExistsException - if the name is already used

      • registerManyEntityProgram

        void registerManyEntityProgram​(String name,
                               Supplier<EntityProgram> programGenerator)
        Register many entity programs of the same type with the given name.
        Parameters:
        name - the name for these programs; must not be null; must be unique
        programGenerator - a generator for the type of program; must not be null; must provide non null programs
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if an argument is null
        ElementExistsException - if the name is already used

        Parameters:

        Returns:
        a set of the names of all entity programs which could be run on this entity

      • getEntityProgram

        EntityProgram getEntityProgram​(String name)
        Get the entity program for a given name.
        Parameters:
        name - The name to get the program for; must not be null
        Returns:

        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if an argument is null
